claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table presenting RT-PCR–confirmed influenza attack rates (n/N and %), relative risk (RR), and relative vaccine efficacy (VE% with 95% CI) for Flublok versus a comparator quadrivalent influenza vaccine across different influenza strains. The figure provides clinical efficacy data (attack rates, RR, and VE) comparing Flublok to a licensed quadrivalent vaccine, but contains no information on antigenic composition or match to WHO- or FDA-selected strains. There is no data or statement regarding sequence identity or antigenic alignment in this table.
